3.0 - **Domain Instrumentation**: ALL domains MUST have custom telemetry
4.0 - **Dashboard Creation**: ALL domains MUST have SigNoz dashboards
5.0 - **Metric Collection**: ALL business metrics MUST be tracked

**❌ ABSOLUTELY FORBIDDEN:**
