### **OpenTelemetry Instrumentation (MANDATORY)**

**✅ REQUIRED INSTRUMENTATION:**
```elixir
# Application startup MUST initialize all instrumentation
def start(_type, _args) do
  # 1. Core telemetry
  Intelitor.Telemetry.attach_handlers()
  
  # 2. OpenTelemetry libraries
  :opentelemetry_phoenix.setup()
  :opentelemetry_ecto.setup([:intelitor, :repo])
  :opentelemetry_oban.setup()
  
  # 3. Domain instrumentation
  Intelitor.Observability.Domains.Alarms.setup()
  # ... ALL domains must be instrumented
  
  # 4. Dual logging validation
  :ok = Intelitor.Observability.DualLogging.validate_dual_logging!()
end
```

