**✅ COMPLIANCE REQUIREMENTS:**
- **100% Hierarchical Coverage**: ALL plans and tasks must use hierarchical numbering
- **Consistent Referencing**: ALL cross-references must use full hierarchical numbers
- **Accurate Rollups**: Status rollup logic must work correctly for all levels
- **Sequential Numbering**: Numbers must be sequential within each parent level
- **Complete Hierarchy**: No orphaned tasks without proper parent context

**❌ VIOLATION CATEGORIES (IMMEDIATE ACTION REQUIRED):**
- **Category 1**: Missing hierarchical numbers (CRITICAL PRIORITY)
- **Category 2**: Incorrect rollup status (HIGH PRIORITY)
- **Category 3**: Inconsistent numbering (MEDIUM PRIORITY)
- **Category 4**: Missing parent references (MEDIUM PRIORITY)
